text:
I'm pretty sure you didn't add what I mentioned above.

Can you remove all additions to the CSS and modify this (in your current CSS):

```@media (min-width: 940px) {
  .franklin-content {
    width: 830px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .franklin-content {
    padding-left: 6%;
    padding-right: 6%;
  }
}```
with this:

```@media (min-width: 940px) {
  .franklin-content {
    width: 830px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  header {
    width: 830px;
  }
}
header {
width: 100%;
padding-left: 12.5%;
padding-right: 12.5%;
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .franklin-content {
    padding-left: 6%;
